    "rule":  "\u0027Doch\u0027 widerspricht einer negativen Frage oder Aussage.",
    "explanation":  "\u0027Doch\u0027 is used to answer \u0027Yes\u0027 to a question that contains a negative. It contradicts the negative bias and confirms the positive state.",
