                                        "type":  "concept",
                                        "title":  "Warum \u0027Doch\u0027?",
                                        "text":  "\u0027Doch\u0027 is a essential German word that has no direct English equivalent. It is used to contradict a negative statement or question with a \u0027Yes\u0027.",
                                        "bullets":  [
                                                        "Ja → positive answer to a positive question",
                                                        "Nein → negative answer to any question",
                                                        "Doch → positive answer to a NEGATIVE question"
                                                    ]
