                                        "to":  {
                                                   "label":  "DOCH",
                                                   "text":  "Doch, ich habe Hunger!"
                                               },
                                        "note":  "English would often just say \u0027Yes\u0027, but German normally uses \u0027Doch\u0027 here to clearly contradict the negative."
